Name: Unassigned
Description: The default status when new objects are created, either directly in the POD or when imported via spreadsheet WITHOUT specifying a pick list.

Name: On Pick List
Description: The item has been added to a picklist.

Name: Boxed
Description: The item has been placed in a box.

Name: Binned
Description: The item has been placed in a bin.

Name: Unpacked
Description: The item has gone through the returns process.

Name: Returned to Unit
Description: The item has been returned to the home unit.
